Advance Digital 





About Advance Digital

		Local Reach, Engaged Consumers

		Advance Digital, Inc. (www.advancedigital.com), based in Jersey City, NJ, is a leading creator of digital news and information products that deliver multi-platform solutions for consumers and advertisers in markets across the United States, in partnership with local media companies affiliated with Advance Publications Inc. Embracing new ideas and innovation, Advance Digital is committed to providing engaging digital solutions that inform, connect and empower the communities it serves. To learn more about our advertising opportunities, click here.

		President: Peter Weinberger
