Advertisement


ShareOverviewSummaryAdvance Publications, Inc. has worked on three contracts worth $11,101 USD in obligations from the federal government since FY2007. In its latest active fiscal year (2009), the organization received a total of $3,039 USD in obligations.The principal agencies it has contracted with are the Department of Veterans Affairs and Department of Defense.

Principal Agencies
Department of Veterans AffairsDepartment of Defense


Principal Category (NAICS)
