The federal government obligated Advance Publications, Inc. a high of $7,225 USD in FY2008 and low of $838 USD in FY2007.* Dollars Obligated: The amount of money obligated towards a vendor by a federal agency or agencies to work on a contract.* Base and All Options (Ceiling): The maximum amount that can be awarded to a contract as mutually agreed upon by the vendor and agency.



