Historical Colors
191 colors inspired by America’s historic landmarks, the Historical Collection has become a favorite for both interior and exterior applications.

See Colors



















































































































































































































Off White Collection
Inherently sophisticated and endlessly versatile, the Off-White collection offers more than 150 variations on white with subtle nuances.

See Colors

































































































































































































Affinity® Color Collection
The 144 colors of the Affinity® Collection are formulated to harmonize with one another and pair beautifully for color flow from room to room. 

See Colors













































































































































































































































































































































Color Stories®
240 full-spectrum colors that are richer, truer and more vibrant than conventional paint colors. Available only in Aura® Interior products.

See Colors

































































































































































































Williamsburg® Color Collection
144 colors that fuse Revolutionary design with Revolutionary paint, bringing Traditional style to Contemporary living.

See Colors



































































America's Colors
42 soft hues inspired by the pale gray of our beautiful coastlines to the rich earth tones of our Southwestern deserts. 

See Colors






















































































































































































































































































































